title: Miniature autumn basket with pumpkin, fly agaric mushrooms and wolfberry branch – 1:12 scale dollhouse fall decor
description: Bring a touch of magical woodland autumn to your dollhouse with this handcrafted 1:12 scale miniature basket. Inside the woven-style basket sits a detailed pumpkin, tiny fly agaric mushrooms, and a delicate wolfberry branch, along with forest leaves and natural textures for an enchanting, storybook feel.
